            <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-[2.9rem]">Build units that overcome any obstacle</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600">Selection and Development for your elite organization is about more than just physical performance. We understand that you are also looking for harder-to-measure attributes.</p>
            <dl class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base/7 text-gray-600 lg:max-w-none">
              <div class="relative pl-16">
