            your Selection and Development process. Our team is made up of former operators, many of whom worked in
            selection and development at the most elite levels.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-300">They will guide you through every stage including:</p>

          <dl class="mt-10 space-y-10">
            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
