                Observing your existing process and learning what makes it unique.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <!-- Heroicon name: outline/check -->
                <svg class="absolute h-6 w-6 text-green-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="ml-9 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-white">
                  Curricula Design
                </p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-9 text-base text-gray-300">
